name: "Double-Decker" sterling silver ring in Gun Metal
description:
It started with the full-finger ring, an ecto-skeletal piece of jewelry that creeps up each digit in chic articulated increments. Then came the upper-finger ring, a tiny band of gold or silver designed to fit snugly above the knuckle. Now a new hybrid, what we’re calling the double-decker ring, is giving traditional bijou a sparkling new companion.

This piece is Sterling silver and is bound to turn heads! 
Can be worn alone or stacked up!!!
